CatDescriptText: Related image published in advertisement in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 22, 1945, pg. 8, with caption reading: "Announcing the Opening of The Rosebud Beauty Salon, 45 Logan Street. Courteous Staff of Efficient, well-trained operators.  Hair Styles to suit Individual Personality.  Complete Facials to perfect complexions.  For appointments, Call Co. 4328. Operators Fannie Berkley, Ruth Oglesby, Maggie Williams, Mattie Rowe.  Mr. and Mrs. Robert Waring, Owners.  Olive Johnson, Manager."
TitMainTitle: Interior of Rosebud Beauty Salon, with six women beauty operators seated in stations, possibly including Fannie Williams wearing three bracelets second from left
